column1: # List of Altinity Stable Build releases. Each line contains three fields
# separated by whitespace: The name of the release, the date of the release,
# and the end-of-life date for that release. When a new point release ships,
# edit the current point release (iow, change 23.8.8.17 to 23.8.11.29, don't
# create a new line), edit the date to the date the point release shipped,
# and edit the end-of-life date if applicable. Which it probably isn't.
